reviews.txt: I liked the final logo - but the process to get there was somewhat of a challenge. The seller didn't read my feedback which resulted in a longer period of revisions. In one comment the seller said they are normally off on Sunday and they would try to get the logo out to me (which they did - and on a Sunday) - but I don't want to hear that. I run multiple businesses. I haven't had a Sunday off in 20 years. Cost of doing business.

Didn't quite get what I wanted, I feel like the result was too identical to the reference image with the only difference being a change of font...but I suppose thats on me for going with the Lite package. Portfolio level images only come standard with the other packages so be mindful. 7/10

Mind Blown! 8 created a logo that far surpassed my expectations. I was given a couple different samples and one tiny change request was all it took. Easy communication and I feel that 8 understood what I was after and really took the idea to the next level. I can't describe how excited I am to use this amazing design. HIGHLY RECOMMENDED!

Seller took 2 days for a partial delivery, then each revision took 1 day, for a total of 10 days to receive my final design. I had to be very specific in my revisions, if things were misaligned or mismatch, the seller will count it as delivered anyways, it is up to you to notice those details and notify the seller. Careful.

Absolutely knockout job from this guy/team! As soon as I saw the final product I jumped out of my chair and showed all of my friends and family immediately! Great communication, patience, and took every step to make the logo of my dreams, but better. I can't wait to book them to make my business cards and social media logos.
